Measure type: [475] Restriction on entry into free circulation
Measure components: Condition [B1] Presentation of a certificate/licence/document : Document [A] Action [28] Declared subheading allowed : ||Condition [B2] Presentation of a certificate/licence/document : Action [08] Declared subheading not allowed :
Conditions:
CD623: (Conditions) Declarations are allowed on this code only if the following condition is fulfilled: presentation of a certificate of authenticity from India or Pakistan in accordance with Regulation (EC) No 972/2006 (OJ L 176). 
Otherwise, another code must be declared.
